snippet.textDisplay:
Kendrick Lamar vs J. Cole
this rivalry is so unique. This is no Tupac or Biggie era but is definitely seems like it. Kendrick group holds down the west coast seriousness. Top Dawg members are consistent and with a tough west coast gangsterness( like nwa or doeboy character) . The east coast J. Cole group creates jazzy and classic drum music. On top Dreamville creates music that is different every time(like a tribe called quest or Bishop). It sounds experimental yet perfected to the most basic form.
